197
00:07:28,980 --> 00:07:33,980
- Risk management, may be the
core most underrated issue

198
00:07:35,070 --> 00:07:37,140
in business for entrepreneurs.

199
00:07:37,140 --> 00:07:38,250
- Risk management?

200
00:07:38,250 --> 00:07:40,980
- Everything has risk, right?
- Yes, of course.

201
00:07:40,980 --> 00:07:43,320
- And it's understanding those risks

202
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:46,440
and mitigating those risks

203
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:50,940
where you may not have the
knowledge base or the experience.

204
00:07:50,940 --> 00:07:54,510
- The fear of failure is a huge
problem in today's society,

205
00:07:54,510 --> 00:07:56,220
and it holds many people back.

206
00:07:56,220 --> 00:07:58,560
Just think if someone can come to America

207
00:07:58,560 --> 00:08:01,890
with is $40 in their pocket,
and become a millionaire

208
00:08:01,890 --> 00:08:05,310
