being bullied by my manager,

211
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:14,040
I wouldn't be wealthy today.

212
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:18,990
All my millions can be traced
back to that one big risk.

213
00:08:18,990 --> 00:08:21,570
Here in the UK, 6 outta 10 people

214
00:08:21,570 --> 00:08:24,840
