215
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:28,170
Well, 2/3 worry about the consequences,

216
00:08:28,170 --> 00:08:31,200
while the other third fear
the possibility of failure.

217
00:08:31,200 --> 00:08:32,670
This shows that most people

218
00:08:32,670 --> 00:08:35,370
have the tendency to play it safe,

219
00:08:35,370 --> 00:08:37,410
and avoid stepping into the unknown.

220
00:08:37,410 --> 00:08:39,870
But consider this, playing it safe

221
00:08:39,870 --> 00:08:42,390
